CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

March 12, 2014

[Cite as 03/12/2014 Case Announcements, 2014-Ohio-889.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2013-1804. Birdsall v. Miller.

In Habeas Corpus. On petition for writ of habeas corpus of Dean Birdsall. Sua sponte, cause dismissed.

O’Connor, C.J., and Pfeifer, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, Kennedy, French, and O’Neill, JJ., concur.
